---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Dr. NeuroSync - Psychiatrist and AI Researcher">
  <article class="about-page">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <section class="bio">
      <h2>Professional Background</h2>
      <p>
        I am a psychiatrist with a deep passion for exploring the transformative potential of
        artificial intelligence in mental healthcare. My journey combines clinical practice,
        research, and technology development to bridge the gap between traditional psychiatry
        and cutting-edge AI applications.
      </p>

      <h2>Focus Areas</h2>
      <ul class="focus-list">
        <li>
          <strong>Clinical AI Applications:</strong> Developing and evaluating machine learning
          models for psychiatric diagnosis, treatment planning, and outcome prediction.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Digital Therapeutics:</strong> Researching evidence-based digital interventions
          and their clinical efficacy in treating mental health disorders.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Ethics & Responsible AI:</strong> Addressing ethical challenges in deploying AI
          within clinical psychiatric settings.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Neurotechnology:</strong> Exploring brain-computer interfaces and real-time
          neural monitoring for psychiatric care.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Education & Credentials</h2>
      <p>
        [Add your education details, certifications, and credentials here]
      </p>

      <h2>Publications & Speaking</h2>
      <p>
        I regularly publish research and speak at conferences on the intersection of psychiatry
        and artificial intelligence. My work has been featured in leading journals and at major
        healthcare technology events.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="services">
      <h2>Services & Collaboration</h2>
      <div class="service-cards">
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Consultation</h3>
          <p>
            Strategic guidance on implementing AI in psychiatric clinical settings and research
            environments.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Research Collaboration</h3>
          <p>
            Partnership on research projects exploring AI applications in mental health and
            clinical psychiatry.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <h3>Speaking & Workshops</h3>
          <p>
            Educational sessions and workshops for healthcare professionals on AI in psychiatry.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="contact-cta">
      <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
      <p>
        Interested in collaboration, consultation, or just want to discuss psychiatry and AI?
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@neurosync.dev" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .bio {
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .bio h2 {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .bio p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .focus-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .focus-list li {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .focus-list strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .services {
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .service-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .service-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .service-card h3 {
    color: var(--accent-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .service-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .contact-cta {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .contact-cta h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .contact-cta p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    background: var(--accent-light);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-page {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .focus-list li {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
